title: Nirvana - Drain You Live and Loud 2013 (kurt's guitar)
description:
For the ones who want to enjoy Live and Loud without Pat Smear guitar.
This mix is a big improvement from my previous torrent

Now:

* 100% sourced from multitrack files
* Bass guitar, kick drum and snare very tight
* Kurt's vocal upfront 
* A warm touch of audience sound (From DTS 5.1 and AC3 5.1 mix)

I will upload Scentless Apprentice again and give you Kurt's Vocals from Live and Loud.

Enjoy!
